		"description": "<p>You can eat and digest huge quantities of food in seconds. Each day, you can nibble off a single Supply Die (of any size). As an action, consume part of the die to gain temporary hit points equal to twice your proficiency bonus. You can nibble on the Supply Die a number of times equal to its size (4 times for a d4, 6 times for a d6, etc). A die which has been nibbled on can’t be used for anything else, and any portion remaining spoils at the end of your next long rest. You can begin to nibble on a new Supply Die when you finish a long rest.</p>",
